name: De Dentro. Autorretrato
description:
"From the insides”. Self-portrait.

This work belongs to the series Mutations. I think I said that Mutations is a key point in my life. It helped me to go through dark moments, but it also emptied me of meaning, I left everything in those works for a long time.
This portrait was really significant for me. It was me, or the version of me at that moment. Of course some of it still remains.

Oil on canvas
Dimensions:  4724 px x 5906 px
Size: 40 x 50 cm
